properties.Name: ChannelRelationshipType
properties.Description:
Describes the nature of the relationship(s) between two or more Channels.

Ex:
- Works for / Is part of / belongs to (channel hierarchy)
- Located in same geographic area
- Compete in same market
- Offer same products
- Replaces

Columns.Name: ChannelRelationshipTypeId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a Channel Relationship Type.

Columns.Name: ChannelRelationshipTypeName
Columns.Description: The name of a Channel Relationship Type.

Columns.Name: ChannelRelationshipTypeDescription
Columns.Description: The description of a Channel Relationship Type.
